Freedom Pacific is a cross-regional international remittance APP. Based on the official standard exchange rate, it provides remittance services in a variety of mainstream currencies. In particular, it solves the inconvenience of remittance to others in areas with few bank branches. At the same time, the collection currency we support is constantly expanding, hoping to bring high quality and convenient use experience to users with international remittance needs.

Freedom Pacific 是一款跨区域的国际汇款APP，基于官方标准汇率,提供多种主流币种的汇款服务，特别是解决了银行网点偏少地区，向他人汇款不便的问题。同时我们支持的收款币种正在不断扩充中，希望给有国际汇款需求的用户带来优质便捷的使用体验。

MATCH, CHAT & DATE. IT STARTS WITH A SWIPE™.
With 97+ billion matches to date, Tinder® is the top free dating app and the best place to meet new people, with safety features that work to help you date more safely. Looking for love? An open relationship? Trying to find a date or new friends to chat with? Connect with local people everywhere on Tinder and get the best out of your dating experience:

Come As You Are: whether you're straight, gay, bisexual or anything in between, you can be who you are and find who you want on Tinder.
Date Beyond Photos: share your interests and learn more about your matches to get the conversation started.
Seek What You’re Looking For: set your relationship goals and make connections on your terms.

HOW TINDER WORKS
It’s easy and fun to find new people on Tinder®. Express yourself to make your personality shine in your profile and stand out to potential matches. Answer a prompt, share a little about you and show your face in your pics to increase your match-making potential. Use the Swipe Right™ feature to like and the Swipe Left™ feature to nope. If they like you back, It’s a Match! And with our double opt-in feature, it’s only a match if the interest is mutual.

PUT SAFETY FIRST
Try some of our safety features to help you make connections more confidently:

– Share My Date: share date plans with friends and fam, so they know who you’re planning to meet up with and where
– Get Photo Verified: verify your photos to help potential matches know it’s really you in that cute pic & increase your chances of matching
– Are You Sure / Does This Bother You: Tinder detects inappropriate language so people think twice before sending a disrespectful message
– Report a Profile: quickly report and block profiles with suspicious activity or inappropriate behaviour
– Block Contacts: take control and block anyone (like an ex) you don’t want to see on the app
– Video Chat: hitting it off in chat? Test your online dating chemistry and meet new people from home!

TRY TINDER PLUS
– Unlimited likes for you to catch feelings for as many new people as you want
– Use Passport Mode™ to match and chat with locals anywhere in the world before you arrive
– Unlimited Rewinds to undo your last like or nope
– Go Incognito and be seen only by the people you like

EXPERIENCE TINDER GOLD
– Get everything in Tinder Plus™, and try it out for a week before you commit to a monthly subscription
– See who likes you and match with them on the spot for faster connections
– Monthly Boost puts your profile to the top for 30 minutes to help increase your profile views
– Weekly Super Likes, because sometimes you really, really like someone

UPGRADE TO TINDER PLATINUM
Get most of Tinder’s premium features: join Tinder Platinum™ to get your likes prioritised with potential matches, send them a compliment before matching and more.

So what are you waiting for? Join millions of people worldwide! Tinder offers the most daters, increasing your chances of finding exactly what you're looking for. Download the best free dating app today!

––––––––––––––––––––
If you choose to purchase Tinder Plus®, Tinder Gold™ or Tinder Platinum™, payment will be charged to your Apple account, and your account will be charged for renewal within 24 hours prior to the end of the current period. Auto-renewal may be turned off at any time by going to your settings in the App Store after purchase. No cancellation of the current subscription is allowed during the active subscription period. If you don’t choose to purchase Tinder Plus®, Tinder Gold™ or Tinder Platinum™, you can simply continue using Tinder for free.

The dating app bringing people closer to love

Bumble is the dating app where people meet, make connections, and start their love stories. We believe meaningful relationships are the foundation of a happy, healthy life — and we're here to help you find yours with a commitment to member safety and tools that empower confident dating.

Match with the right people, date, and find meaningful connection

Bumble is a free app for meeting singles and building connections grounded in mutual respect and trust. Whether you’re ready to find the one or date for fun, Bumble can help you connect with real people to build something authentic.

As champions of love, we prioritize creating a space where our members feel respected, confident, and empowered to make connections

- Our members are at the heart of everything we do
- We put safety first — so you can date with confidence, knowing you’re connecting with verified matches
- Respect, courage, and joy guide how we show up — and inspire others to do the same

Try our free features — built to make dating easier
- For better connections, conversations, and dates, personalize your profile with interests and prompts to showcase who you are, what you’re into, and what you’re looking for
- Trust that the person you’re talking to is real with ID Verification
- Feel confident with expert-backed dating advice designed to help you succeed
- See what music you bond over by linking your Spotify account
- Video chat and share your favorite pictures with your matches to get to know them better
- Chat with peace of mind — knowing that when you’re talking to new people, all messages must meet our community guidelines
- Get extra reassurance by sharing the details of your meetups with someone you trust
- If you’re ever in need of a dating break, hide your profile with the Snooze Mode (you'll still keep all your matches)

Want even more ways to connect? Bumble Premium unlocks extra features to boost your dating experience
- See everyone who likes you
- Use Advanced Filters like “What are they looking for?” to meet people who share your values, hobbies, and goals
- Rematch with expired connections — so you don’t miss out on a great potential date
- Browse anonymously with Incognito Mode and only seen by who you want to see you
- Extend your matches by 24 hours
- Swipe as much as you like to meet more people
- Tap into dating scenes around the world with Travel Mode
- Stand out and get noticed with free SuperSwipes & Spotlights, refreshed weekly

Inclusivity is key
At Bumble, we promise to support and include all forms of love: straight, gay, lesbian, queer, and beyond. We want everyone in our community to feel safe and welcome. So no matter how you identify, if you're looking for a place to chat, date, and find real love, we’ve got what you’re looking for.

---
Bumble is a free dating app to download and use. We offer optional subscription packages (Bumble Boost & Bumble Premium) and non-subscription, single, and multi-use paid features (Bumble Spotlight & Bumble SuperSwipe). Your personal data is securely processed in line with our privacy policy and applicable laws—be sure to read our privacy policy and terms and conditions.

https://bumble.com/en/terms

Looking for information about someone—a celebrity, influencer, or a person you just met? Ask DeepScope, an AI-driven, all-in-one people search assistant that helps you discover accurate details about anyone in seconds. Simply type a name and get verified information, photos, and social media profiles—all in one place. 

What’s inside the app: 

• SMART NAME SEARCH 
Start with a simple query—just enter the name of the person you’re looking for. DeepScope instantly searches across multiple sources, verifies the results, and builds a clean, easy-to-read profile card for you. Plus, you can always refine your query by adding extra details and help the app find the exact match. 

• VERIFIED INFORMATION  
No more unreliable results. Each search is checked and cross-referenced, so you can explore accurate, up-to-date info about the person you’re looking for—from background facts to public details. 

• PHOTO GALLERY 
View relevant images to confirm you’ve found the right person. With DeepScope, you can see different images pulled from open sources, social media, and more. 

• SOCIAL MEDIA AND PUBLIC PROFILES  
Easily access direct links to a person’s online presence. Supported platforms include YouTube, Wikipedia, Instagram, Facebook, X (formerly Twitter), TikTok, LinkedIn, and more coming soon. All the profiles you need—in one convenient place. 

• SMART HISTORY 
All your previous searches are saved for quick access. You can revisit profiles, review answers, or delete your entries anytime. 

Why DeepScope? 
Because finding information about others shouldn’t take hours. Whether you’re verifying a public profile, discovering new creators, or simply satisfying your curiosity, DeepScope makes it fast, accurate, and effort-free. 

Start your search today! Discover people, explore profiles, and find the connections that matter—all in one click with DeepScope at hand. 

Premium Subscription 
• Subscribe for unlimited searches and access to all advanced features. 
• Subscriptions are billed automatically at the rate depending on the selected plan (weekly, monthly, or annual). 
• Manage your subscription and turn off auto-renewal anytime in your Apple ID account settings after purchase. 

By using the app, you agree to our Privacy Policy and Terms of Use:

https://aiby.mobi/ai_search/terms/

Циан — ведущий сервис в России для тех, кто ищет недвижимость для аренды или покупки. Здесь можно легко найти жилье на короткий или длительный срок, а также предложения по продаже квартир, домов и коммерческих объектов. 

Наш сервис предлагает широкий выбор жилья как в новостройках, так и на вторичном рынке, включая уникальные проекты квартир и детальные планировки. Все объявления проходят модерацию, что гарантирует их актуальность и достоверность.

Более 80 фильтров для удобного поиска квартир и домов
Ищите квартиры и дома для покупки или аренды с помощью интерактивной карты в приложении — просто выберите нужный район. Более 80 фильтров помогут найти подходящий вариант с учетом инфраструктуры и характеристик жилья. Фильтруйте по цене, количеству комнат и другим параметрам. Сохраняйте поиск и добавляйте понравившиеся объекты в избранное, чтобы не упустить выгодные предложения от собственников без скрытых комиссий.

Широкий выбор квартир в новостройках
Просто задайте параметры поиска: срок сдачи ЖК, этаж, площадь, наличие или отсутствие отделки, а также цену за всю квартиру или за квадратный метр. Если вы предпочитаете покупку от застройщиков или вам важна комнатность вашей квартиры, для вас доступны специальные фильтры. Таким образом, вы сможете легко найти свой идеальный ЖК.

Умный Циан-помощник для поиска недвижимости
Циан-помощник — интеллектуальный сервис, который покажет подходящие варианты, поможет с ипотекой, сообщит о новых объявлениях, сэкономит время и поможет принять решение. Поручите поиск жилья искусственному интеллекту — задавайте критерии, а помощник пришлет вам подходящие варианты.

Оформление ипотеки
Заполните одну анкету и отправьте её сразу в 7 банков — всего за 2 минуты вы получите персональные предложения по ипотеке. Сравните условия и выберите то, что подходит именно вам. Ипотека — это первый шаг к вашему будущему дому или квартире. Начните путь к мечте уже сегодня!

Посуточная аренда квартир, домов и коттеджей
Удобный поиск жилья для посуточной аренды — квартиры, дома, коттеджи и комнаты. Смотрите варианты на карте или в списке, фильтруйте по цене, району, типу и удобствам. Легко сравнивайте объекты и выбирайте лучшее - в центре, у метро, у моря или рядом с достопримечательностями.

Размещение объявлений о сдаче и продаже недвижимости
Размещайте объявления о продаже или аренде недвижимости любого типа. В личном кабинете доступны инструменты для общения с покупателями и арендаторами — звонки, чат и поддержка агентов, которые помогут на всех этапах сделки.

Поиск коммерческой недвижимости для вашего бизнеса
Арендуйте или покупайте коммерческую недвижимость, подходящую под все ваши бизнес-потребности, включая офисы, склады, и торговые помещения. Удобные фильтры помогут быстро найти подходящий вариант по нужным параметрам. Сервис предоставляет широкий выбор предложений под разные цели и бюджеты.

Быстрая и бесплатная оценка недвижимости
Узнайте рыночную цену квартиры, дома или другой недвижимости быстро и бесплатно. Получите данные о кадастровой стоимости, текущих арендных ставках и истории цен по интересующему объекту. Это поможет точно оценить стоимость, выгодно инвестировать и принять обоснованное решение при продаже, покупке или аренде.

Если недвижимость, то Циан!

Know what’s happening at home wherever you are with Ring Video Doorbells, Security Cameras, Alarm systems and Ring Intercom. Ring Video Doorbells and Security Cameras can send you instant alerts when someone’s at your door or motion is detected. Keep an eye on what matters with live HD video and greet visitors with Two-Way Talk. With a Ring Home Plan subscription (or free trial), you can review, save and share Ring videos.

With Ring Intercom, you can speak to whoever is at your building entrance and buzz them in using the Ring app.

Ring Alarm systems let you monitor entrances and indoor spaces. Enrol in Ring Alarm Calls (compatible Ring Home Plan subscription required) to trigger automated calls to your emergency contacts when a security issue is detected.

Whether you’re halfway around the world or just popping out to the shop, with Ring, you’re always home.

What you can do with the Ring app:

- Get real-time doorbell and motion alerts on your smartphone or tablet
- See and speak with visitors with live HD Video and Two-Way Talk
- Get real-time alerts when your Alarm sensors are triggered

Chat & Date is the most easy to use dating app to find amazing people near you, and let them find you too 

See how popular you and your friends are, as well as a list of the great people nearby, wherever you may be; at a music festival, on college campus, or hanging out in the city. We also give you all the tools so that, whether you're looking for a relationship, friendships or to find love, you can do it no fuss, no complications. 

Download Chat & Date to meet new people and start your straightforward dating journey 

WHY CHAT & DATE? 
We are the dating site that consistently ensures safety and respect within our community. We do not tolerate any kind of inappropriate behavior and have strict usage guidelines, as well as an extensive list of safety features to ensure that you have the best dating experience with us. 

WE MAKE DATING EASY 
We make it easier to meet people near the way you want to meet them... 

- Dating Nearby: Meet singles around you or make new friends. 
- Encounters: Straightforward swiping, right to show you're interested and left to keep swiping. 
- Video Chat: Connect with your matches through face to face video calling. 
- Verified profiles: Chat safer and choose to only interact with verified profiles. 
- Blur intimate photos: We automatically detect explicit photos and warn users before they open them. 

CHAT & DATE PREMIUM 
Serious about dating honestly? Then activate the Premium mode to access plenty of new, exciting features that will help you get the most out of our app to meet, chat and date with amazing people: 

- Find out who added you to their favorites and meet singles. - See who liked your profile. It's time to meet new people and find friends! 
- Get your messages read first. 
- Swiped left on the person of your dreams? You can go back with Premium! 


____________________________ 

The price varies by country and may change without notice, but you can always see the exact price in the app. We will charge your card and your subscription will be automatically renewed unless you deactivate the automatic recharge a minimum of 24 hours before the end of your current subscription period. Know the future and hidden secrets about yourself and others with accurate palm readings and analysis. Read the Life line, Head line, Heart line, Success Line, Fate Line, Travel Line, and Marriage line. Know more about love life, quality of life, health, personality, married life, etc. for your loved ones. Totally Free fun app. Be the center of attention in any party or group of friends by reading their palms.

The ancient practice of Chiromancy can help you reveal a lot about your past, present, and future. Aren't we always eager to know what life has to offer? 
Well, now you can at least get a clue and work towards your goals accordingly.

Through the Palmistry app, you will get to know about:
- Love Life
The Heartline will help you know about your love life and also guide you in the same.
- Physical Strength | Quality of Life | Health
The Life line is a future teller and helps you know how you will be able to improve your quality of life and health.
- Personality
The Head line will tell you what kind of a person you are and whether it is bad or good for your life.
- Marriage Life
The Marriage line will tell you how your married life will be and how to make it better if you are married and facing problems by reading the palm lines.
- Career | Work Life | Struggle & Success 
Do you feel you put in all the effort you can in a certain task and yet don't succeed in your career or elsewhere? Let the Success line show you what is wrong.
- Destiny | Luck & Fame
The Fate line reveals what life has in store for you in general and whether it is about money or personal issues.
- Travel 
The Travel line can reveal a lot about your travel thoughts and motivate you to travel and make traveling plans for the future.

You simply need to follow the instructions on the screen, answer a few questions about your palm, and get detailed reading quickly.

The Bible: God’s Living Word for Salvation, Transformation, and Eternal Hope

The Bible is more than a book—it’s the living Word of God, filled with divine wisdom, eternal truth, and unshakable promises that guide us through every season of life. Through daily Bible reading, prayer, and reflection, we draw closer to God, discovering His boundless love, grace, and purpose for our lives. We are on a mission to share the Bible with the world, and we warmly invite you to join this divine movement. 

Why Study the Bible?
The Bible is God’s love letter to humanity. It reveals His plan for salvation through Jesus Christ, teaches us how to live according to His will, and offers hope, comfort, and guidance in every circumstance. By studying Scripture, we grow in faith, deepen our understanding of God’s character, and learn to trust His promises. 

What You’ll Experience with the Bible App:
1. Daily Prayer
Join millions of believers around the world in morning and evening prayers. Lift up your family, friends, and personal needs to the Lord—whether it’s your marriage, career, relationships, or future. Pour out your heart to God and experience the peace that comes from connecting with Him daily.

2. Bible Verses & Devotionals
Receive daily Bible verses paired with beautiful images and inspiring devotionals. Immerse yourself in powerful Bible stories, Scriptures, and worship music that bring God’s Word to life. Grow in faith, humility, and wisdom as you reflect on His teachings and share them with loved ones.

3. Bible Chat: AI-Powered Bible Study & Q&A
Unlock the depth of Scripture with advanced AI tools designed to enhance your Bible study experience.

Verse Interpretation: Get clear, insightful explanations of Bible verses, helping you understand their historical context, theological meaning, and practical application.

Ask Questions: Have questions about the Bible? Our AI-powered Q&A feature provides accurate, biblically sound answers to your spiritual inquiries.

Personalized Insights: Receive tailored recommendations for verses and passages based on your spiritual journey and current needs.

Deep Dive into Scripture: Explore cross-references, commentaries, and thematic studies to gain a richer understanding of God’s Word.

Life Application: Learn how to apply biblical teachings to your daily life, relationships, and challenges.

4. Prayer Topics for Every Need

Love & Relationships: Strengthen your marriage, friendships, and family bonds.

Hope & Faith: Find encouragement in God’s promises.

Forgiveness & Healing: Experience God’s mercy and restoration.

Overcoming Challenges: Conquer anxiety, depression, fear, and anger.

Peace & Rest: Prayers to calm your mind and help you sleep.

Career & Purpose: Seek God’s guidance for your work and life goals.

Health & Healing: Pray for physical, emotional, and spiritual healing.

Spiritual Growth: Deepen your relationship with God and live out His calling.

If you haven’t yet experienced the Bible App, Download the Bible App today and carry God’s Word with you wherever you go.. Every time you read, listen, meditate on, or share God’s Word, you are participating in His divine plan to transform hearts and lives.

The MTM Status is the first hybrid smartwatch that combines the look and functionality of a traditional watch with abilities that are evident in today’s smartwatches. Discreetly housed in the casing of a classical timepiece is technology that keeps tabs on your daily activity, provides traveler with local and world time/weather,  integrates with the Health app, turn-by-turn navigation, in addition to hot keys for Camera/Music control/Find My Phone features and even a sophisticated mechanical compass. Of course, the watch handles smartphone notifications seamlessly.

The heart of the analog is not a traditional movement but a state of the art “triple bi-directional gearbox”, which means the developer can configure the traditional watch hands (hour, minute and second) to do much more that telling time (e.g. compass and event alert). 

Smart and discreet, MTM is the smartwatch of choice for anyone who appreciates the value of complications in a traditional timepiece, yet, enjoys the functionalities of a day to day smartwatch.”

description:
Alice AI: texts, neural network, fresh ideas, knowledge, Russian-language AI chat.

Powerful Yandex AI on your phone helps with everyday chores and tackles tasks for study, work, and creativity.

Explore what the neural network can do with Alice—everything you expect from a smart chat in Russian.

Alice AI is Yandex’s family of generative models that power Alice. It includes:
- Alice AI LLM — a language model for answering questions and generating text;
- Alice AI ART — an image model for creating visuals;
- Alice AI VLM — a multimodal vision-language model for analyzing images, answering questions, and solving image-related tasks.

Ask questions, write and edit text—the Alice AI neural network responds accurately and comprehensively, and can enrich answers with images and source links. Speak by voice or type in chat.

Work with files (DOC, DOCX, PDF, TXT), structure information, and turn it into clear, usable reports. The Alice AI assistant quickly extracts key insights.

Work with photos—recognize text in images, identify objects, and get fast visual analysis. The AI chat assistant can pull data from a receipt photo, explain what’s in a shot, and convert it into an editable text format for further use.

Solve complex problems—reasoning mode produces not just quick and detailed answers, but thoughtful conclusions. You get well-founded solutions with expert-level analysis.

Create compelling English-language copy, ask questions, translate, and edit. Yandex Alice’s AI assistant helps draft anything—from personal emails and school assignments to business proposals.

Find inspiration: generate new project ideas, run brainstorms, craft descriptions and messages, and build your own text templates. Let Alice handle the routine. The AI assistant can write a letter, a script for an event or talk, suggest a post title, or even a name for your pet.

Create images and AI video—Yandex ART generates visuals or animates photos on request. Alice helps you produce striking social posts, a logo, or a birthday card.

Use AI chat for professional work. The assistant helps with programming and code, offering multiple solution approaches. Alice AI teaches logic, explains logical problems clearly, and shares interesting facts. Get advice and recommendations on any topic—Alice answers in detail, suggests step-by-step actions, and helps you plan.

Ask questions, type text, attach photos, videos, and files—or talk through the camera in real time with Live Mode. With the Pro option, show Alice what you see in Live Mode and get instant answers and ideas. Just open the Alice AI app and point your phone’s camera at whatever you want to learn about.

Alice AI can be your guide to landmarks, your kitchen co-pilot for “what can I cook with this?”, or your stylist for picking shoes to match your trousers. Ask anything and switch topics as needed. The neural network keeps context, recognizes objects in the frame, and delivers fast, in-depth answers.
